				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "7WxtJEAHR1ObXn5csxzMgw=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# Step 1: Register an App in Azure AD\n\n- Go to Azure Portal.\n- Navigate to Microsoft Entra Id > Manage > App registrations > New registration.\n- Give it a name (e.g. Intune App Extract), and select the correct supported account types.\n- Click Register\n# Step 2: After registering:\n\n- Save Application (client) ID\n- Save Directory (tenant) ID\n- Client credentials > New Client secret and store it securely.\n# Step 3: Add API Permissions\n\n- Go to Manage > API permissions for your app registration:\n- Add permission: Microsoft Graph > Application permissions > Select permissions\n- Add DeviceManagementApps.Read.All\n- DeviceManagementManagedDevices.Read.All (optional for broader info)\n- Click Add Permission\n- Click \"Grant admin consent for \" and authorize the account"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-03-24T12:41:34.663677-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-03-24T12:41:34.663677-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "cEYxIPYiT6C7I9SuU+9fkQ=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Store your credentials in `~/.secrets/intune-graph-config.json` (see {{gtClass:IntuneGraphClientExamples}} >> {{gtMethod:IntuneGraphClientExamples>>#clientConfig}}):\n```\n{ \"tenantId\": \"your-tenant-id\", \"clientId\": \"your-client-id\", \"clientSecret\": \"/path/to/secret.txt\" }\n```"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "pharoSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
