					"uidString" : "uMcB63uzRLK9yPzGQ+cmHA=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "## Using IntuneGraphClient\n\nThe above steps are handled automatically by {{gtClass:IntuneGraphClient}}, which manages token acquisition and expiry-based caching. See {{gtPage:IntuneGraphClient}} for full documentation."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "pharoSnippet",
				"children" : {
